description: & then I learned that the spiritual journey has nothing to do with being nice. It was bout being real, authentic. Having boundaries. Honoring MY SPACE first & others second. & in this space of self care, being nice just happened.... it flowed.... not motivated by fear but by love... #NiceTry 🙋🏼‍♀️✌🏻🏄‍♀️💓🌱
